The paper deals with the problem of discovering unusual events in videos, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method utilizes trajectory analysis, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also involves machine learning techniques for classification, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
